"{\"uid\": \"today.com-news-paris-olympics-simone-biles-goat-necklace-paris-olympics-2024-rcna164774\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A Michael Kors Bag, Suede Slippers and More Holiday Gifts at Walmart - Starting at $9    Liz Calvario  Editor/Reporter  Simone Biles knew that people \\\"would go crazy\\\" over her goat necklace and they did.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\", \"score\": 0.9999990301914905, \"rank\": 9.69809391006174e-07, \"text\": \"Michael Kors\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old gymnastics superstarwon gold in the women's gymnastics all-around finalon Aug. 1, marking her second gold medal during the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asshe nabbed her sixth gold medaland ninth overall, Biles cemented herGOAT-\\u00a0Greatest of All Time - status by showing off her latest medal alongside her necklace that included a diamond-encrusted goat charm.\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles spoke about the significance of the necklace during a press conference with reporters that same day.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My GOAT necklace is just kind of an ode, because the people love it and some people hate it,\\\"she said.\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 779, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, it's like the best of both worlds.\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was like, 'OK, if it goes well, we will wear the GOAT necklace.'\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know people will go crazy over it.\\\"\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 924, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Adding, \\\"But at the end of the day, it is crazy that I am in the conversation of 'greatest of all athletes' because I just still think, 'I am Simone Biles from Spring, Texas, that loves to flip.'\\\"\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 1094, \"end\": 1099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"score\": 0.8368404569850734, \"rank\": 0.15053784403955234, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It should be noted that at 27, Biles is the oldest U.S. Olympic gymnast in 72 years, according to NBC News.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"People in the comments section applauded Biles and encouraged her to own the GOAT status.\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\", \"score\": 0.7168567345960191, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GOAT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yassss wear the necklace and pop yo 'ishhh\\u2026.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have earned it Sis,\\\" one person wrote, while another added, \\\"You are Simone Biles from Spring Texas who loves to flip to the point of Olympic Gold.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1468, \"end\": 1473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"score\": 0.8368404569850734, \"rank\": 0.15053784403955234, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are an inspiration to the world!\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"God Bless.\\\"\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's so humble!\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's another reason why we love her so much!\\\"\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1637, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"one fan wrote.\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another commented, \\\"She is the once in a lifetime athlete!\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Deserving of all the praise and respect!!\\\"\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The goat necklace was commissioned by the athlete from Janet Heller Fine Jewelry, who shared in anInstagrampost that the piece is \\\"a three-dimensional masterpiece adorned with 546 diamonds\\\" and \\\"embodies her unparalleled status in gymnastics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 2000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1812, \"end\": 1817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janet_Jackson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.25034374683395e-18, \"text\": \"Janet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janet_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janet_Jackson\"}, {\"begin\": 1988, \"end\": 1998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999992120284253, \"rank\": 6.250312137124031e-07, \"text\": \"gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The jeweler noted that they also designed a bespoke Olympic rings necklace for Biles.\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The pieces are \\\"a testament to the enduring legacy of a true champion.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2158, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the Paris 2024 Olympics unfold, all eyes are on Simone Biles - the GOAT both on and off the mat.\\\"\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And on the mat, Biles' outstanding floor routine secured her the all-around first place win.\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brazil's Rebeca Andrade took home the silver, while defending U.S. gold medalist Suni Lee nabbed the bronze.\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2354, \"end\": 2360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.9669770545540655, \"rank\": 0.03228672981736959, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 2363, \"end\": 2377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}, {\"begin\": 2416, \"end\": 2425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/U.S._Gold\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"U.S. gold\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/U.S._Gold\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/U.S._Gold\"}, {\"begin\": 2435, \"end\": 2443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Suni Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The win comes after Team USA